<br>
Acrylia Plate: (trivs start in low 200s and max at 242 with the breastplate)<br>
<br>
1. combine acrylia temper (brew triv 122)<br>
-- essence of wind (Air Elementals in Twilight Sea; Crag Li &amp; Meeda Hune Soldiers, Warlords, Tenebrous Mts; Crag Li, Scarlet Desert )<br>
-- crushed windstone (Grimlings (several types), Crag Li &amp; Meeda Hune Soldiers and Warlords, Tenebrous Mts; Moktar Tribesmen, Umbral Plains; an Earth Element, Twilight Sea)<br>
-- vial of clear mana (kidnap lvl 29 'chanter)<br>
2. acrylia chain jointing (smithy triv 116)<br>
-- acrylia rings (smithy triv 75)<br>
- - - large brick of acrylia (uhhh Bazaar, heh)<br>
- - - flask of water<br>
- - - file<br>
-- water<br>
-- combine smithy hammer<br>
-- file<br>
3. leather padding (LQ pelt and thread, tailoring triv 31)<br>
4. appropriate plate mold (merchant)<br>
5. appropriate number of folded acrylia sheets (smithy triv 116)<br>
-- 1 block of acrylia (go back to the Bazaar again, drop too many places to list here)<br>
-- water<br>
-- smithy hammer <br>
6. Combine smithy hammer<br>
<br>
bracer, collar, visor: 1 folded acrylia sheet <br>
vambraces, helm, girdle, gauntlets, boots, pauldrons: 2 folded acrylia sheets <br>
breastplate, greaves, cloak: 3 folded acrylia sheets <br>
