<br>
One mistake that Hybrids can make is going for caster stats.  If you focus on caster stats, particularly in non visible armor items (silver ruby veil instead of cougarskin mask on face), for example.  You will be well served in filling all your armor spots with gear that has AC, HP, Stamina, and then in descending order Strength/agility/dexterity.  Take what wisdom you get by accident and you will generally be in good shape mana wise as a hybrid.  <br>
<br>
<br>
Most bang for plat, has to be the goranga idol now.. Range item 8 ac plus melee stats including hitpoints... less than 200 pp in bazaar on twenty different sellers.<br>
